               stealing two hempen cloths, value 6 d. 3 lb. of lump sugar, value 2 s. eight oz. of green tea, value 2 s. 6 d. a pair of stone sleeve buttons set in silver, value 4 s. one plumb cake, value 2 s. and a yard of silk ribbon, value 6 d.
